</P>
<P>
   A1668 BC-QUOTE-OF-THE-DAY-NYT 91 20:53 R A
</P>
<P>
   QUOTATIONS OF THE DAY
</P>
<P>
   A1667 BC-DOMESTIC-VIOLENCE-AZR 948 20:52 R A
</P>
<P>
   TRYING TO KILL SPOUSE WAS TURNING POINT FOR SHELTER FOUNDER
</P>
<P>
