   REAL-LIFE _ WEST PALM BEACH, Fla. _ Here's why a mother named
Patricia Fowler Bouton is my new idol: She actually listened when
her son came out of his room one night and said he couldn't sleep
because he was hearing noises. Turned out it's a good thing she did
because there was a man, a burglar, asleep under the kid's bed.
(Minor, Palm Beach Post) MOVED.
