<P>
   LEEMAY-COLUMN _ Copperhill, Tenn. _ Eat your heart out, New
York. While hot dog vendors are being legislated off the streets of
Gotham, here in the Copper Basin, Raymond Arthur, hot dog maker
extraordinaire, still basks in the glow of appreciation. (May,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution) MOVED. EMBARGOED UNTIL 6/11.
</P>
