<HEADLINE>
SNAKEBITES MAY NO LONGER NEED RADICAL PLASTIC SURGERY 
</HEADLINE>
   (To publish this ``separate buy'' article from the London-based
science and technology weekly NEW SCIENTIST it must be purchased --
the rate is not prohibitive -- from one of these New York Times
Syndicate sales representatives: 
 (--U.S., Canada and the Pacific: CONNIE WHITE in Kansas City,
816-822-8448 or fax her at 816-822-1444.
 (--Europe and Asia: KARL HORWITZ in Paris at 47-42-17-11; fax,
47-42-80-44 or 47-42-18-81; telex, 282-942. 
 (--Mexico, Central America, South America: PAUL FINCH in Los
Angeles, 310-996-0075; fax, 310-996-0089. 
