<HEADLINE>
COUPLE FOLLOWED TRADITIONAL MUSLIM RULES 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by N.Y. Times News Service clients)  
 By KELLY ETTENBOROUGH  
 c.1998 The Arizona Republic  
