<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-06-10 13:54 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2795 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u d &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-FOOD-NANCY-BOS &LR;      06-10 1569
