</P>
<P>
   BKN-NBAFINALS (Chicago) _ The Chicago Bulls hope to take a
commanding 3-1 lead in their best-of-seven series with the Utah
Jazz Live in Game 4 of the NBA Finals. By EDDIE SEFKO.
</P>
<P>
   SOC-WORLD-CUP (Paris) _ Defending champion Brazil beats Scotland
2-1 in the opening match of the World Cup soccer competition. By
JOHN P. LOPEZ.
</P>
<P>
   BBN-ASTROS (Detroit) _ The first-place Houston Astros go for
their fifth consecutive victory as they try to complete a
three-game sweep of the Detroit Tigers. By JOSEPH DUARTE.
</P>
<P>
