   DEATH-WATCHERS &QL;
</P>
<P>
   UNDATED _ When a pre-written obituary about entertainer Bob Hope
became public, it not only stirred up the masses, it aroused a
rather morbid bunch on the Internet. It grabbed the attention of
celebrity death-watchers. For those unfamiliar with this Internet
sect, celebrity death-watchers take part in or manage macabre
online contests for fun and/or cash prizes. By TOMMY CUMMINGS.
Story will move in ``l'' lifestyle category. &QL; 
.MDNM/ DOLLAR-COIN &QL;
