<P>
   ARAB AMERICANS
</P>
<P>
   Total population in U.S.: 3 million
</P>
<P>
   ETHNIC:
</P>
<P>
   Lebanese: 1.4 million
</P>
<P>
   Syrian 433,000
</P>
<P>
   Egyptian 267,000
</P>
<P>
   Palestinian 164,000
</P>
<P>
   Iraqi 79,000
</P>
<P>
   Jordanian 70,000
</P>
<P>
   Arab 433,000
</P>
<P>
   Other 84,000
</P>
<P>
   RELIGION:
</P>
<P>
   Orthodox/Protestant 30 percent
</P>
<P>
   Roman Catholic 30 percent
</P>
<P>
   Muslim 30 percent
</P>
<P>
   Other 10 percent
</P>
