anyone of the candidates is a front runner is inaccurate.'' Says
the process will go well into next week. Jackson's agent says there
has been no formal contact by the Sonics, but if there is an
official inquiry, Jackson is happy to listen and that Jackson
definitely is interested in a multi-year deal (if he doesn't return
