</P>
<P>
   DRUGS-ECONSCENE (Undated) _ If the war on drugs is indeed a
battle of good vs. evil, then Satan is gaining some impressive
allies. An open letter to the U.N. secretary-general, on the
occasion of the General Assembly's special session on drugs,
asserts that ``the global war on drugs is now causing more harm
than drug abuse itself.'' By Peter Passell.
</P>
<P>
   (Scheduled to move by 8 p.m. ET.)
</P>
</TEXT>
