<HEADLINE>
BOB HOPE STORY BRINGS CELEBRITY DEATH-WATCHERS BACK TO LIFE
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By TOMMY CUMMINGS 
c.1998 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
<TEXT>
