<HEADLINE>
 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by N.Y. Times News Service clients)  
BC- ELIMINATE_ELIMINATE-AZR
<TEXT>
<P>
   EDITORS:
</P>
<P>
   Budgeted Phoenix BABY-GUILT will not move in Thursday's Arizona
Republic report.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
<TRAILER>
NYT-06-10-98 2037EDT &QL; 
</TRAILER>
