<HEADLINE>
IBM ELBOWS ITS WAY INTO A GROWING SPECIALTY CHIPS MARKET
</HEADLINE>
 
(EDS: Adds tagline with Web note at end) (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By MARK P. COUCH 
c.1998 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
<TEXT>
<P>
   FORT WORTH, Texas _ Texas Instruments is getting some more
