   Marcelo Salas
</P>
<P>
   Country: Chile. Age: 23.
</P>
<P>
   Position: Striker.
</P>
<P>
   Club team: River Plate (Argentina).
</P>
<P>
   Notes: ``The Matador'' is one half of the lethal Za-Sa forward
combination, joining Ivan Zamorano to lead Chile to its first World
Cup since 1982. The star of River Plate's three straight Argentine
championship teams, Salas will play next season for Lazio in Italy
after being transferred for $21 million. Has scored 19 goals in 31
international matches.
</P>
